---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Locus:
    Page: 237
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
Among the sages of the past
are there any who survived
they lived and then they died
all turned to dust and ashes
their piled-up bones would match Vipula
their tears of parting form a sea
their empty names alone remain
none escaped the Wheel of Birth and Death
